# Fortran Guide

an outline organizing Fortran Wiki subjects with an eye towards teaching Fortran

Please pick a missing topic and add links to pertinent files or create them.
AI may ultimately replace the need for a User manual by being a superior reference
or by writing code itself, but that time is not yet. AI can be leveraged to create
many of the missing topics, which is an interesting exercise in itself. And of
course, writing missing sections and reorganizing this index is encouraged as well.

